No Internet Connection

  Problem
User reported no internet access on their workstation, while other devices were working normally.

  Diagnosis
- Checked physical connections (Ethernet cable and ports)  
- Verified IP configuration using ipconfig  
- Identified incorrect IP assignment (no valid gateway)  

  Solution
- Renewed IP address using network commands  
- Restarted network adapter  
- Verified correct DNS and gateway configuration  

  Result
Internet connection was restored, and the user was able to resume work without further issues.
